      <title>伊斯兰国声称对伊朗致命爆炸事件负责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/islamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-deadly-iran-blasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊斯兰国声称对周三在伊朗发生的袭击事件负责，该袭击造成近 100 人死亡，并有可能进一步加剧中东紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/islamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-deadly-iran-blasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 17:13:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
