      <title>由于霍乱死亡人数激增，赞比亚推迟了学年开始时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/zambia-delays-start-of-school-year-as-cholera-deaths-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着赞比亚霍乱死亡人数不断攀升，赞比亚将学年开学推迟了三周，与 2018 年 1 月采取的措施相呼应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/zambia-delays-start-of-school-year-as-cholera-deaths-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 12:50:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
