      <title>伊朗致命爆炸和红海警告加剧中东紧张局势</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/deadly-iran-blasts-and-us-warnings-escalate-mideast-tensions</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊朗表示，中部省份造成近 100 人死亡的爆炸事件很可能是自杀式炸弹袭击者所为，此前这起袭击引发了人们对中东冲突扩大的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/deadly-iran-blasts-and-us-warnings-escalate-mideast-tensions</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 06:30:00 GMT</pubDate>
